## User Collection [/user]

### Create a New User [POST]

You may create your user.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
                "userName": "John",
                "sytem": {
                    "id": "a39d14cd-7058-4e16-8f4a-a7f923f87e4b",
                    "name": "Nintendo Switch",
                },
                "games": {
                    "id": "e643d072-9d74-40e2-b10e-21e10b866e25",
                    "name": "Pokemon Sword",
                },
                "pokemon": {},
                "conversation": {}
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /

    + Body

            {
                "userName": "John",
                "sytem": {
                    "id": "a39d14cd-7058-4e16-8f4a-a7f923f87e4b",
                    "name": "Nintendo Switch",
                },
                "games": {
                    "id": "e643d072-9d74-40e2-b10e-21e10b866e25",
                    "name": "Pokemon Sword",
                },
                "pokemon": {},
                "conversation": {}
            }

### Create a New User Pokemon [POST]

You may create your own user Pokemon.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "userId": "1c562767-10fe-4c7f-bc2b-9125112e72b1",
            "name": "Venusaur",
            "shiny": true,
            "gender": {
                "type": "female",
                "amount": "87.5",
            },
            "pokeType": "grass",
            "abiliity": {
                "name": "Chlorophyll",
                "hidden": true,
            },
            "eggMoves": ["Skull Bash", "Petal Dance", "Curse", "Ingrain"]
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /1c562767-10fe-4c7f-bc2b-9125112e72b1/pokemon

    + Body

            {
                "userId": "1c562767-10fe-4c7f-bc2b-9125112e72b1",
                "name": "Venusaur",
                "shiny": true,
                "gender": {
                    "type": "female",
                    "amount": "87.5",
                },
                "pokeType": "grass",
                "abiliity": {
                    "name": "Chlorophyll",
                    "hidden": true,
                },
                "eggMoves": ["Skull Bash", "Petal Dance", "Curse", "Ingrain"]
            }
            
